== Where it stands ==

The system is in Alpha — **fully operational end-to-end**, not yet production-ready. Everything is **open source, non-profit, and transparent**.

== What I'm looking for ==

* **Fact-checkers and newsrooms** willing to test the tool and share feedback
* **Research partners** for joint projects
* **Foundations and sponsors** who believe independent fact-checking infrastructure matters

